{"tid":1634031,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔仔飼養心得，日常交流","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T11:59:54.000Z","uid":197098,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e48c41487c07d265fc6d7b366de73bb21a809f38","tid":1634031,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auVQySB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FauVQySB.jpg&h=a3fafe69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v9vQySW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv9vQySW.jpg&h=abd8a422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n建議用貓廁所，一半放乾草，一半放墊材(e.g. Carefresh 紙綿) 夠大和舒適，牠會開心地跳入去使用，不需任何訓練。<br />\n<br />\n用圍欄圍住籠- 加大空間，貓廁所放入圍欄內，每天放牠出來 living room一段時間周圍探索。放出來前記得用膠管包住電線，兔仔大機會會咬破，我在IKEA 買，中文名叫整線器:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FKmz0M7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFKmz0M7.jpg&h=d4d77d0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1WwiyQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1WwiyQ.jpg&h=c672996b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住同牠絕育呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f46e4c205a195844597a1f20b8bd4b42bd6717","tid":1634031,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"歡迎兔友post自己兔仔D相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7960eeb2f77c913ea88ca0ca216f94409eb9817","tid":1634031,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:46:16.000Z","msg":"Post 你老母車頭相啦"},{"pid":"6776094a49df1a4b21cc8aa378494136aae73191","tid":1634031,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兔子是應該要被絕育</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 兔子是被捕獵動物(Prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(Predator)的目標, 狗吠聲、消防車叫聲、小孩尖叫、雷暴等也會嚇驚兔子, 所以不建議帶出外散步。兔子是全世界其中一個最多被棄養的動物(在美國排第3最多被棄養), 很多人將牠放生, 這樣會令兔子十分恐慌, 而且沒有覓食能力(寵物兔和野兔是不同), 有些人送給兔協, 但容納不到那麼龐大的數目。<br />\n<br />\n2. 絕育後會大大減少因荷爾蒙控制而霸地盤，不會隨地去廁所 (兔子是不需要訓練去廁所，只要廁所內有紙棉和乾草和夠大便可以, 建議用貓廁所)<br />\n<br />\n3. 荷爾蒙減少令攻擊性減少，更加溫馴和親人，也會活得更開心。如果想將2隻兔合養(做夫妻/好朋友)要先絕育才容易建立關係, 否則有機會打架！<br />\n<br />\n4. 兔子是很容易患上生殖器病動物，所以絕育會令到更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5. 減少過量繁殖(和棄養後所面對的困境)，繁殖得快和多。"},{"pid":"4a43ef091548067a85a06da53ac06c80549da112","tid":1634031,"uid":202889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:23:02.000Z","msg":"你隻兔好cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相more"},{"pid":"26eafe41940665b0bf9810d44e9b976d75c04185","tid":1634031,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a43ef091548067a85a06da53ac06c80549da112","tid":1634031,"uid":202889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:23:02.000Z","msg":"你隻兔好cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相more"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:58:16.000Z","msg":"Thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你也有養嗎？"},{"pid":"f0d16ba22a18fc73e2ad2448d90559d45efb4fd2","tid":1634031,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:14:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">8</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">提款日</span></span></strong><br />\n各大銀行總行撳錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">9</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣日</span></span></strong><br />\n齊齊修補連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">10</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">